      • TEST

        public static final int TEST
        The constant TEST is used to indicate the evaluation type in the context of testing. The value TEST signifies that the evaluation is carried out solely for testing purposes and has no impact on the user interface (UI). This is useful for distinguishing evaluation options performed within the testing framework.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
